# Phase 6 IBKR news fixtures land here.
#
# When the user runs `cargo run --bin ibkr_news_spike --features ibkr-spike`
# against a TWS / Gateway with news subscriptions enabled, this directory
# fills with:
#   - news_providers.json
#   - AAPL_historical.json
#   - AAPL_article_<id>.json
# See loop/plan/phase-6-ibkr-news-spike.md and loop/plan/notes/ibkr-news-shape.md.
